Hello everyone! :wave:

I am running into an indexing issue with CTAs that I was looking to get help with. With the embedded image CTAs we have created on the new builder (not legacy), it looks like the redirect URLs from the tracking are being flagged in Ahrefs as not indexable (see screenshot).

This has come up for almost all of our clients' sites - is this something that is pointing to a larger issue with the new CTA builder or is there a way around this?
so sorry I didn't reply <@UF6M5BW4C> - I don't think you can programmatically update the HubSpot sitemap, it's all manual one page at a time.
